fucking mutt in the history of the Mafia.

1657
02:13:24,756 --> 02:13:27,554
Even if this thing is a Federal boat, Left,

1658
02:13:29,160 --> 02:13:32,561
they scam all these other people.
They didn't scam us.

1659
02:13:32,663 --> 02:13:34,460
You know what I'm saying?

1660
02:13:36,000 --> 02:13:38,468
We went. We had a great party.
We walked away from it.

1661
02:13:41,905 --> 02:13:45,136
