- I'll be all right.

1674
02:14:37,612 --> 02:14:40,638
Did I say you was a rat?
I can't believe you brought that up.

1675
02:14:40,749 --> 02:14:42,512
Come on. Forget about it, Left.

1676
02:14:42,617 --> 02:14:44,881
I never said you was a rat.

1677
