and this check for $500.

1728
02:22:31,867 --> 02:22:33,300
Hold the check up.

1729
02:22:34,369 --> 02:22:37,634
- Congratulations again, son.
- Congratulations, Joe.

1730
02:22:38,941 --> 02:22:41,967
- Ma'am, take good care of him.
- I will.

1731
02:22:42,344 --> 02:22:43,811
Mrs. Pistone.

